overview.en: DeepBrainChain was established in November 2017. The vision is to build the world's largest distributed high-performance computing network based on blockchain technology and become the most important infrastructure in the 5G+AI era
overview.zh: 深脑链成立于2017年11月，愿景是基于区块链技术构建全球最大的分布式高性能算力网络，成为5G+AI时代最重要的基础设施
